overview.longBusinessSummary: Evolent Health, Inc., through its subsidiary, provides specialty care management services in oncology, cardiology, and musculoskeletal markets in the United States. The company offers integrated platform for health plan administration and value-based business infrastructure. It also provides administrative services, such as health plan services, pharmacy benefits management, risk management, analytics and reporting, and leadership and management; and Identifi, a proprietary technology system that aggregates and analyzes data, manages care workflows, and engages patients. In addition, the company provides holistic total cost of care management; and Machinify Auth, a software platform that leverages advances in artificial intelligence. Evolent Health, Inc. was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Arlington, Virginia.
